<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This book resolves EVERYTHING. It is the poster child of resolution. Everything changes, everything (even tiny insignificant details from book 1) play<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This book resolves EVERYTHING. It is the poster child of resolution. Everything changes, everything (even tiny insignificant details from book 1) plays a part in shaping what becomes of the world. Read it. Read it now. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
