  <span id="freeText1178909540080830599" style="display:none">Thank you for this review. I just finished the Trilogy. While i love info-dumps, got really sucked into the story and had a good time guessing what would happen next, i got so frustrated by the way Vin and the other female characters are treated. Since Vin was the only developed female character, i hoped she would survive. yet in the end, she was kinda insignificant. And those other female characters, they were laughable! so shallow, it was frustrating to read. also they were always described from a male perspective. the only female perspective in this epic story died in the end, i hated that.</span>
