        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3736920748" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer559420357664459122">I’ve never been more sad over finishing a series. These characters had become everything! This series felt like nothing but a guide to do fantasy right. Will always remain among few of the books close to my heart 💕 </span>

          </span>
